                    <p class="fst-italic">Neurology s a branch of medicine dealing with disorders of the nervous system.</p>
                    <p>During a neurological examination, the neurologist reviews the patient's health history with special attention to function of the cranial nerves (including vision), strength, coordination, reflexes, and sensation.</p>
                    </div>
