                    <p class="fst-italic">Pediatrics is the branch of medicine that involves the medical care of infants, children, and adolescents.</p>
                    <p>The body size differences are paralleled by maturation changes. The smaller body of an infant or neonate is substantially different physiologically from that of an adult.</p>
                    </div>
